con:config.con:query: SELECT M.INITIATORBANKID,M.CUSTOMERID,TRANSACTIONSID,M.AGREEMENTID,PAYMENTINFOID,HT.DEBETACCOUNTNO,PAYMENTSTATUS,INSTRUCTEDAMOUNT FROM MESSAGE M INNER JOIN PAYMENTINFO PI ON M.MESSAGEID = PI.FK_MESSAGEID INNER JOIN HST_TRANSACTIONS HT ON PI.PAYMENTINFOID = HT.FK_PAYMENTINFOID WHERE M.INITIATORBANKID='4201' and PAYMENTSTATUS='COMP' --and INSTRUCTEDAMOUNT='20' ORDER BY TRANSACTIONSID DESC fetch first row only
